parameters: \TA[1]You can learn skills from your senpai.

\TA[1]Tasks will become available over time, but you need to learn
skills to enhance your tasks.

\TA[1]Skills have various effects and can enhance your tasks in
unique ways.

\TA[1]In addition to funds, there may be other conditions required
to acquire skills.
\TA[1]Use your funds effectively to acquire skills.
\TA[1]By selecting a day of the week, you can choose a schedule.

\TA[1]Schedules can be selected with the directional keys (left
and right), and the amount of money earned and fatigue
consumed varies for each.

\TA[1]On special days such as holidays and anniversaries, there is
a fixed schedule and you cannot choose other schedules.

\TA[1]When you select a schedule, the estimated total amount of
money earned is displayed at the bottom right of the screen.

\TA[1]Once all schedules are selected, the confirm button becomes
active, and confirming the schedule will start the schedule
for the week.
\TA[1]You can take a break on the weekends as well.

\TA[1]Taking a break will recover your fatigue level. The
efficiency of recovery depends on the skills you've learned.

\TA[1]While you cannot perform regular duties, you can explore the
company.

\TA[1]As you continue to explore, you can find resources and
useful items.

\TA[1]If you have enough energy left, it might be a good idea to
go exploring.
What should I do this weekend...
\TA[1]I will explain the resources used in the game.

\TA[1]Magic power is the goal of the game and the most crucial
resource for Saki's survival.

\TA[1]The purpose of this game is to collect magic power
efficiently using various methods.
\TA[1]Magic power is also necessary when acquiring new skills.

\TA[1]Experience points are a resource needed for self-
improvement.
\TA[1]They are also used for acquiring new skills.

\TA[1]Magic power and experience points can be obtained from the
weekly schedule.

\TA[1]While checking the remaining days, let's try to collect
resources efficiently.

\TA[1]From now on, all Friday tasks will be fixed to "Business
Partner Tasks."

\TA[1]Working with a business partner yields more resources than
general tasks and comes with specific effects.

\TA[1]Increasing your trust level with the business partner allows
for leveling up, which enhances the resources gained and the
effects of buffs.

\TA[1]If certain conditions are met, another business partner will
be unlocked. Each business partner has different resources
and buff effects.

\TA[1]Furthermore, you will be able to choose a business partner
for weekend explorations in the future.

\TA[1]As trust increases, more locations within that business
partner will become available for exploration.

\TA[1]Manage your relationships with business partners well to
maintain a harmonious partnership.

\TA[1]From now on, the quota of magical power needed for each
quarter will be set.

\TA[1]The ultimate goal of this game is to efficiently gather
magical power so that Saki can survive without being
forcibly dispatched.

\TA[1]A quarter is 3 months (13 weeks), and a total of one year is
given until the game's ending.

\TA[1]Please lend your strength so that Saki can survive safely in
this black company.
\TA[1]I will explain the game interface and the main currency.

\TA[1]In the top right corner of the screen, you can see your
current magical power and experience index.

\TA[1]Magical power is the goal of the game and the most crucial
resource for Saki's survival.

\TA[1]The objective of this game is to efficiently gather magical
power using various methods.
\TA[1]Magical power is also needed when acquiring new skills.

\TA[1]The experience index is a resource necessary for self-
improvement.
\TA[1]It is also used in the acquisition of new skills.

\TA[1]In the bottom right corner of the screen, the current
fatigue level is displayed.

\TA[1]The more fatigue you accumulate, the lower the success rate
of schedules becomes.

\TA[1]In the bottom left corner of the screen, the remaining time
period is displayed.
\TA[1]All tutorials can be reviewed again later from your senpai.
